body:
The root of the website will always be from the latest stable version, which is currently 1.0.
Your changes in master will be deployed under `https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/master/get_started/get_started`.
Your changes will also be in the next release cut which will be 1.2 (1.1 is already cut, and nearing the final release.)
